Big Brother Naija reality star, Nengi has clarified reports of her encounter with Ozo in the bathroom. Recall that Eric said Ozo and Nengi had their bath together during the reality show. However, Nengi during her media rounds on Friday said she was never naked with Ozo in the bathroom. According to the Bayelsa-born housemate, she was fully clothed in the bathroom with Ozo. “I was fully clothed with Ozo in the bathroom, so it was not a big deal for me,” Nengi said.